: 187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe for just$49.95$32.50!\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just$49.95$32.50\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A NOTE FROM THE PUBLISHER: When the Olympic organizers and others on the Left use the term 'inclusive,' they mean prioritizing those who have contempt for Christianity.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999999600713261, \"rank\": 3.992867125689473e-07, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A NOTE\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 285}, {\"ngram\": \"THE PUBLISHER\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 304}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"the Left\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"the term\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusive\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"contempt\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The key to \\\"apologizing\\\" without really apologizing is to use the wordif, as in, \\\"If I have offended you, I am deeply sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The key\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"the wordif\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of us have first-hand experience with this technique - on the giving and receiving ends.\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 669, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"first-hand experience\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"this technique\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"the giving\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"ends\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has a 100% failure rate.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 100% failure rate\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What's more, it generally makes the offended party feel even more aggrieved.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the offended party\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exhibit A is the statement that Olympics spokesperson Anne Descamps made over the weekend in the wake of worldwide outrage over the blatant mockery of the Last Supper during the Paris Games' drag queen-themed opening ceremonies on July 26.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Exhibit A\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the wake\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"worldwide outrage\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"the blatant mockery\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games' drag queen-themed opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group,\\\" she said, adding, of course, \\\"If people have taken any offense, we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"any offense\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Translation: We are only sorry that so many Christians are too backward to grasp the artistic genius of what we have done.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1230, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999963315080082, \"rank\": 3.6323460717045784e-06, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the artistic genius\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are multiple themes present in the Gospel accounts of the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gospel\", \"score\": 0.999992612481495, \"rank\": 6.467006448903889e-06, \"text\": \"Gospel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gospel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gospel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple themes\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of them is betrayal.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of us felt precisely that when we watched something so sacred to Christians - particularly Catholics, because of our belief in and reverence for the Eucharist - denigrated in a historically Catholic country like France, the erstwhile Eldest Daughter of the Church and the homeland of St. Th\\u00e9r\\u00e8se, St. Joan of Arc and the Little Sisters of the Poor.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999963315080082, \"rank\": 3.6323460717045784e-06, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.77949939324908e-17, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.835619932667894e-16, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9915693440105902, \"rank\": 0.007973499412857285, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1705, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Th\\u00e9r\\u00e8se_(film)\", \"score\": 0.6885601169068543, \"rank\": 0.264743589743583, \"text\": \"Th\\u00e9r\\u00e8se\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Th\\u00e9r\\u00e8se_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Th\\u00e9r\\u00e8se_(film)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"our belief\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"reverence\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"the Church\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"the homeland\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"St. Joan\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"Arc\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"the Little Sisters\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"the Poor\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was something undeniably demonic about what we witnessed.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The devil, we know, uses imitation to mock God.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The devil\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"imitation\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We got an unpleasant taste of that when the Los Angeles Dodgers honored the drag-queen \\\"Sisters of Perpetual Indulgence\\\" last year.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Dodgers\", \"score\": 0.9999976841008434, \"rank\": 2.2893542537370186e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Dodgers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Dodgers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Dodgers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unpleasant taste\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"the drag-queen \\\"Sisters\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1974}, {\"ngram\": \"Perpetual Indulgence\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremonies multiplied that scandal by a factor of 50.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"that scandal\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"a factor\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How do we respond?\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First, we need to wake up.\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When the Olympic organizers and others on the Left \\\"celebrate inclusivity,\\\" they do not mean that term in the way Webster's defines it.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"the Left\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"that term\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"Webster's defines\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather, the intent is to promote the views and agendas of everybodyother than thosewho espouse traditional Christian beliefs.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999975029823, \"rank\": 2.4969857643951024e-09, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intent\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"the views\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"agendas\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"everybodyother\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"thosewho\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or more precisely, prioritizing and praising those who have contempt for those values.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contempt\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"those values\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Second, is there anyone you know who might assume that, though you are Catholic, youwouldn'tbe offended by a mockery of the Last Supper?\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"a mockery\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2591}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If so, you need to set them straight.\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sadly, too many Catholics have lost their sense of the sacred, especially regarding the Mass and the Real Presence.\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2667, \"end\": 2676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.77949939324908e-17, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their sense\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mass\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"the Real Presence\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is the point of the National Eucharistic Revival, to call us back to a spirit of humble gratitude and awe for Jesus' enduring sacrifice.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2882, \"end\": 2887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999242554651, \"rank\": 7.574443588320178e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2784}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Eucharistic Revival\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2820}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2832}, {\"ngram\": \"a spirit\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2849}, {\"ngram\": \"humble gratitude\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"awe\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We saw the fruits of this effort manifested in amazing ways at the National Eucharistic Congress in Indianapolis, especially the record-setting downtown procession where all were welcome to honor Our Lord - an outpouring of devotion we will see again in September at the International Eucharistic Congress in Ecuador.\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2985, \"end\": 3005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.067859028242481e-20, \"text\": \"Eucharistic Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\"}, {\"begin\": 3009, \"end\": 3021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9999999999472493, \"rank\": 3.799954264803643e-11, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}, {\"begin\": 3180, \"end\": 3214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2919358829502145e-20, \"text\": \"International Eucharistic Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\"}, {\"begin\": 3218, \"end\": 3225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.400989078338531e-16, \"text\": \"Ecuador\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fruits\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"this effort\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"amazing ways\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the record-setting downtown procession\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3072}, {\"ngram\": \"Our Lord\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"an outpouring\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3129}, {\"ngram\": \"devotion\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now it's time to put this rekindled devotion into action.\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3240}, {\"ngram\": \"this rekindled devotion\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The timing of the outrage in Paris, coming so close on the heels of the Eucharistic Congress in Indianapolis, is no coincidence, any more than the fact that it happened on the same weekend when the Gospel readings at Mass begin to focus on Jesus' Bread of Life discourse.\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3315, \"end\": 3320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999948399818, \"rank\": 5.160193573883167e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3358, \"end\": 3378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.067859028242481e-20, \"text\": \"Eucharistic Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharistic_congress\"}, {\"begin\": 3382, \"end\": 3394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9999999999472493, \"rank\": 3.799954264803643e-11, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}, {\"begin\": 3484, \"end\": 3490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gospel\", \"score\": 0.999992612481495, \"rank\": 6.467006448903889e-06, \"text\": \"Gospel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res